    "name": "GCPro - Mission APIs",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for testing Mission APIs\n\n**Available APIs:**\n1. Mission.Publish - Publish a draft/paused mission\n2. Mission.ApproveSubmission - Approve a mission submission\n\n**Authentication:**\n- X-User-Id: User ID header\n- X-User-Role: User role (ADMIN, REVIEWER, USER)\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Update {{base_url}} variable to your server URL\n2. Run SQL scripts to insert test data\n3. Update mission_id, submission_id variables with your test data",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
