      "name": "Mission.ApproveSubmission",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Approve Submission (Success)",
          "id": "0fe2dcd6-217a-48e9-a71b-e7e24ff4f03f",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Id",
                "value": "{{admin_user_id}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Role",
                "value": "ADMIN"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"approve_test_{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"approval_note\": \"Great submission! Proof looks good.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/missions/{{mission_id}}/submissions/{{submission_id}}/approve",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "v1",
                "missions",
                "{{mission_id}}",
                "submissions",
                "{{submission_id}}",
                "approve"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Approves a pending mission submission.\n\n**Prerequisites:**\n- Submission must exist with status='PENDING'\n- Enrollment must have status='SUBMITTED'\n\n**Expected Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"submission_id\": \"987f6543-e21b-43d1-b098-765432109876\",\n  \"submission_status\": \"APPROVED\",\n  \"enrollment_id\": \"456f7890-a12b-34c5-d678-901234567890\",\n  \"enrollment_status\": \"COMPLETED\"\n}\n```\n\n**Side Effects:**\n- Submission → APPROVED\n- Enrollment → COMPLETED\n- 3 events emitted (including MISSION_REWARD_REQUESTED)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Approve with Reviewer Role",
          "id": "674c572a-6339-4123-9ffa-86591c07448e",
          "request": {
